metadata.title: Pyle Cable Protector Floor Cover Ramp - 1 Channel Cable Protector Rubber Floor Cord Concealer - Heavy Duty Cable Protector Wire/Hose/Pipe Hider Driveway Protective Covering Armor - PCBLCO102X2 (Pair)
features: PROTECTIVE CABLE CONCEALMENT: Rugged, reliable and durable cable cover ramp that is safe and ideal for high “walking-traffic” areas. It comes in black and bright yellow color to provide high visibility and additional safety to passers-by

WATERPROOF MATERIAL: The cable protector features marine grade waterproof construction. Comes in non-interfering style for wheels and carts to roll over w/ ease. This heavy duty cable ramp can be used in homes, offices, schools, stores or warehouses

11, 000 LBS LOAD CAPACITY: The cord track concealer is made of highly durable engineered thermoplastic rubber. It weighs only 3. 75 lbs. but boasts 11, 000 lbs. maximum load capacity making it safe for pedestrian walking and lightweight vehicle traffic

SUPERIOR WIRE PROTECTION: Efficiently provides superior protection for cables, wires, extension cords, hoses, tubes, pipes, etc. It features interlocking male/female connector system for hassle-free cable placement. Ideal for indoor and outdoor use

WIDE CHANNEL GROOVE DESIGN: The protective cover comes in 1 wide channel groove to allow enough rooms for multiple floor cables and power cords. Connectors allow for additional/external unit assembly. Each cable ramp measures 39. 6’’L x 8. 7’’W x 1. 2’’H
description: Cable Protector Cover Ramps - Cord/Wire Safety Concealment Floor Tracks with Flip-Open Access Lid, Rugged & Waterproof, Indoor/Outdoor Use (Single Channel Grooves) (Pair) Features: Hassle-Free Cable Cover Ramps Universal Cord / Wire Protector Tracks Safely Conceals Cables, Wires, Cords, Hoses, Tubes, Pipes, etc. Rugged & Durable Construction Easy Access ‘Flip-Open’ Hinge Lid Single Channel Concealment Track Design Marine Grade Waterproof Rated Construction Interlocking Male/Female Connector System Connectors Allow for Additional / External Unit Assembly Safe for Pedestrian Walking & Lightweight Vehicle Traffic Used for Home, Office & Business Applications Indoor/Outdoor Use What's in the Box: (2) Cable Cover Ramps Technical Specs: Cable Cover Ramp Style: Single, One-Channel Grooves Maximum Support Weight: Up to 11, 000 lbs. Load Capacity Construction Material: Engineered Thermoplastic Rubber, Reinforced ABS Maximum Cable Diameter/Thickness Compatibility: 20mm Diameter Single Channel / Groove Size (W x H): 2. 83’’ x 0. 8’’ -inches Total Cable Ramp Size (L x W x H): 39. 6’’ x 8. 7’’ x 1. 2’’ -inches (Each) Sold as: Pair Weight: 20. 92 lbs.
